{
  "lesson": "WC-12-05",
  "audioMaster": "training/module12-settings/WC-12-05-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 288.131,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Start in Settings, and open the Hardware group.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.209,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Five lists live here, and together they describe the machines at a wash:",
      "startS": 2.209,
      "endS": 6.393,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "the terminals that exist, the screen layouts they run, and the lube-bay buttons they show.",
      "startS": 6.393,
      "endS": 10.848,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Think of this as the field tech's corner of Settings,",
      "startS": 10.848,
      "endS": 14.323,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "the place you check before you touch anything at the site.",
      "startS": 14.323,
      "endS": 17.36,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Click Hardware / Terminals.",
      "startS": 17.76,
      "endS": 18.978,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Every machine a wash runs shows up here as one row:",
      "startS": 18.978,
      "endS": 22.944,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "its location, its address on the network, the build it runs, and when it last checked in.",
      "startS": 22.944,
      "endS": 28.389,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "When a site reports a dead register, start here.",
      "startS": 28.389,
      "endS": 31.907,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "A terminal that isn't listed, or whose last-seen time is hours stale,",
      "startS": 31.907,
      "endS": 35.876,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "has already told you something.",
      "startS": 35.876,
      "endS": 37.398,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "The rows didn't load today, so read the columns.",
      "startS": 37.398,
      "endS": 40.818,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Now Screen Layout.",
      "startS": 41.28,
      "endS": 42.57,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "This one loaded.",
      "startS": 43.019,
      "endS": 44.043,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "The tiles count six layouts, split evenly between POS and kiosk,",
      "startS": 44.47,
      "endS": 52.127,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "and each row pins a screen type and a resolution to a location.",
      "startS": 52.559,
      "endS": 56.251,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "A portrait kiosk, a landscape register, each with its own entry.",
      "startS": 56.888,
      "endS": 57.513,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "One quirk: the card claims six records but lists two.",
      "startS": 57.778,
      "endS": 60.232,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Trust the tiles for the real count, and treat the rows as samples.",
      "startS": 60.696,
      "endS": 64.042,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "System Types is next.",
      "startS": 64.48,
      "endS": 65.969,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "It's a short lookup list, one description per row,",
      "startS": 66.384,
      "endS": 69.454,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "the kind of behind-the-scenes list other pages point at.",
      "startS": 69.783,
      "endS": 72.836,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Nothing to configure day to day.",
      "startS": 73.16,
      "endS": 78.729,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Today it didn't load either, so note what it is and move on.",
      "startS": 79.833,
      "endS": 82.769,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "When you see \"failed to fetch\" on a page like this, it's the data service, not an empty list.",
      "startS": 83.045,
      "endS": 85.562,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Lube Buttons.",
      "startS": 86.06,
      "endS": 87.236,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Here's button wiring at its plainest.",
      "startS": 88.048,
      "endS": 90.219,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Twenty-four buttons across a few lube-bay terminals, one row each.",
      "startS": 90.638,
      "endS": 94.946,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "The row names the group it belongs to, the terminal it appears on,",
      "startS": 95.532,
      "endS": 97.402,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "the label the operator taps, and the tile's color.",
      "startS": 97.746,
      "endS": 102.357,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Oil Change in teal, Tire Rotation in blue.",
      "startS": 103.002,
      "endS": 104.23,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "When someone says a lube button is wrong, this is the row you read.",
      "startS": 104.617,
      "endS": 110.535,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Lube Checklists.",
      "startS": 111.011,
      "endS": 111.613,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "One column, the service.",
      "startS": 111.613,
      "endS": 113.271,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "These are the checklist items a lube bay works through on a job.",
      "startS": 113.271,
      "endS": 117.587,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Like System Types, it didn't load today,",
      "startS": 117.587,
      "endS": 119.979,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "so read the column and the purpose, not the values.",
      "startS": 119.979,
      "endS": 122.991,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "A menu tour like this is about knowing where each list lives,",
      "startS": 122.991,
      "endS": 126.96,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "so that when a ticket points here you go straight to it.",
      "startS": 126.96,
      "endS": 130.574,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Collapse Hardware, and open UI and Display.",
      "startS": 131.04,
      "endS": 133.889,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Eleven lists this time.",
      "startS": 134.791,
      "endS": 136.139,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Most are the paint and the plumbing: button types, images, colors, templates.",
      "startS": 136.479,
      "endS": 138.028,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "We'll read the ones a technician gets asked about:",
      "startS": 138.323,
      "endS": 141.331,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "the cashier and greeter buttons, the button groups behind them,",
      "startS": 141.841,
      "endS": 143.986,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "the macros, and the kiosk screen flows.",
      "startS": 144.583,
      "endS": 150.628,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "The rest are the lookups those five draw from.",
      "startS": 151.258,
      "endS": 153.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Button Groups.",
      "startS": 153.76,
      "endS": 154.742,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "A group is just the named set a button is filed under,",
      "startS": 155.445,
      "endS": 158.455,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "the same group value you saw on the lube buttons a moment ago.",
      "startS": 158.898,
      "endS": 162.193,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Two columns, a description and whether it's active.",
      "startS": 162.617,
      "endS": 165.516,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "It didn't load today, so read the shape.",
      "startS": 165.836,
      "endS": 167.936,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Groups are the folder; the buttons are what's inside.",
      "startS": 168.455,
      "endS": 171.298,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "Cashier Buttons.",
      "startS": 171.76,
      "endS": 172.832,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "These are the tap targets on the register screen.",
      "startS": 173.196,
      "endS": 175.953,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Each row is a button: its slot number, its label,",
      "startS": 176.507,
      "endS": 177.729,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "the kind of action it runs, and its tile color.",
      "startS": 178.079,
      "endS": 182.867,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "So \"the void button moved\" or \"the wrong color\" is answered right here, one row per button.",
      "startS": 183.352,
      "endS": 188.199,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "The list didn't load today, but the columns tell the story.",
      "startS": 188.562,
      "endS": 193.1,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "Greeter Buttons.",
      "startS": 193.52,
      "endS": 194.108,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Same four columns, aimed at the greeter station out at the lane instead of the register.",
      "startS": 194.108,
      "endS": 199.355,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Keeping the two lists apart lets a site put different buttons",
      "startS": 199.355,
      "endS": 203.515,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "in front of the greeter than the cashier.",
      "startS": 203.515,
      "endS": 206.75,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "If a lane's entry screen looks wrong, you check here, not the cashier page.",
      "startS": 206.75,
      "endS": 210.863,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "This one didn't load today either.",
      "startS": 210.863,
      "endS": 213.28,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "Macros.",
      "startS": 213.68,
      "endS": 213.973,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "A macro is a saved action a button or a scanned barcode can fire.",
      "startS": 213.973,
      "endS": 218.47,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "The columns tell you its type, whether a barcode triggers it,",
      "startS": 218.47,
      "endS": 222.128,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "and whether it also shows on the handheld.",
      "startS": 222.128,
      "endS": 224.47,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "That last one matters when an operator says a shortcut works",
      "startS": 224.47,
      "endS": 227.691,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p70",
      "text": "at the register but not on the handheld device.",
      "startS": 227.691,
      "endS": 230.538,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p71",
      "text": "It didn't load today, so read the columns.",
      "startS": 230.538,
      "endS": 232.88,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p72",
      "text": "Last list: Kiosk Screen Flows.",
      "startS": 233.28,
      "endS": 234.121,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p73",
      "text": "This is where self-serve kiosk screens are built and pushed live.",
      "startS": 234.465,
      "endS": 235.932,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p74",
      "text": "The tiles count three flows, two published and one draft, across eleven screens.",
      "startS": 236.489,
      "endS": 240.191,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p75",
      "text": "Each row is a flow: its locations, how many screens and tappable hotspots, and a status chip.",
      "startS": 240.893,
      "endS": 242.42,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p76",
      "text": "Read the chip first.",
      "startS": 242.711,
      "endS": 246.109,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p77",
      "text": "Published is live on the kiosks;",
      "startS": 246.697,
      "endS": 252.756,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p78",
      "text": "a draft, like Express Tunnel, is built but not out yet.",
      "startS": 253.3,
      "endS": 254.641,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p79",
      "text": "The create button here reads New Flow.",
      "startS": 255.262,
      "endS": 263.68,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p80",
      "text": "So that's Hardware and UI and Display.",
      "startS": 264.171,
      "endS": 266.772,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p81",
      "text": "Hardware registers the machines and their screens.",
      "startS": 267.494,
      "endS": 270.138,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p82",
      "text": "UI and Display wires the buttons a cashier and greeter tap,",
      "startS": 270.494,
      "endS": 275.627,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p83",
      "text": "the macros behind them, and the kiosk flows a site publishes.",
      "startS": 275.962,
      "endS": 278.332,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p84",
      "text": "Two groups, ten lists, all read-only for you.",
      "startS": 278.956,
      "endS": 282.453,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p85",
      "text": "Learn where each one lives, because a POS ticket usually ends on one of these pages.",
      "startS": 282.842,
      "endS": 287.631,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}